quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  89,1,Vel fecri
  89,2,Ve leyalin ﾂｴaﾅ殲in
  89,3,Veﾅ淒歹fﾂｴﾄｱ velvetri
  89,4,Velleyli iza yesri
  89,5,Hel fiy zalike kasemﾃｼn liziy hﾄｱcrin
  89,6,Elem tere keyfe feﾂｴale rabbﾃｼke biﾂｴadin
  89,7,ﾄｰreme zatilﾂｴﾄｱmadi
  89,8,Elletiy lem yuhlak mislﾃｼha fiylbiladi
  89,9,Ve semudelleziyne cabussahre bilvadi
  89,10,Ve firﾂｴavne ziylﾂｴevtadi
  89,11,Elleziyne taﾄ歛v fiylbiladi
  89,12,Feekseru fiyhelfesade
  89,13,Fesabbe ﾂｴaleyhim rabbﾃｼke sevta ﾂｴazabin
  89,14,ﾄｰnne rabbeke lebil mirsadi
  89,15,Femmelﾂｴinsanﾃｼ iza mebtelahﾃｼ rabbﾃｼhu feekremehu ve naﾂｴamehu feyekulﾃｼ rabbiy ekremeni
  89,16,Ve emma iza mebtelahﾃｼ fekadere ﾂｴaleyhi rizkahu feyekulﾃｼ rabbiy ehaneni
  89,17,Kella bel la tﾃｼkrimunelyetiyme
  89,18,Ve la tehaddune ﾂｴala taﾂｴamilmiskiyni
  89,19,Ve teﾂｴkﾃｼlunettﾃｼrase eklen lemmen
  89,20,Ve tﾃｼhﾄｱbbunelmale hubben cemmen
  89,21,Kella iza dﾃｼkketilﾂｴardu dekken dekken
  89,22,Ve cae rabbﾃｼke velmelekﾃｼ saffen saffen
  89,23,Ve ciyﾂｴe yevmeizin bicehenneme yevmeizin yetezekkerﾃｼlﾂｴinsanﾃｼ ve enna lehﾃｼzzikra